Package: opsctl
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: opsctl maintainers <root@localhost>
Depends: libc6, ca-certificates, adduser
Description: Local deployment safety gate for AI-assisted Debian servers
 opsctl keeps local server facts, deployment plans, approvals, snapshots,
 audit logs, and read-only AI integration outputs in one small CLI/TUI tool.
 It is intended for single Debian servers where AI coding tools deploy over SSH.
